# =============================================================================
# File: /opt/ansible-k3s-cluster/README.verification-pipeline
# =============================================================================
# Purpose:
#   Document the verification pipeline used after deploying a new kernel or
#   modifying cluster configuration. This ensures cluster consistency and
#   operational readiness.
#
# Verification Steps:
#
#   1. Kernel Verification
#        ansible-playbook kernel-verify.yml
#
#   2. Node Health Check
#        ansible-playbook cluster-health.yml
#
#   3. Service Status Check
#        ansible-playbook cluster-service-report.yml
#
#   4. Kernel Report
#        ansible-playbook cluster-kernel-report.yml
#
#   5. dmesg Review
#        ansible-playbook cluster-dmesg-report.yml
#
# Notes:
#   - This pipeline should be run after every kernel deployment.
#   - Ensures nodes are healthy, consistent, and ready for workloads.
# =============================================================================
